### 31) Moldessa

- Location: Hard Mode (Ruins)
- Quick summary: Hard Mode mold creature; evolved form with stronger attacks.
- Attacks / Behavior: Larger slime drops, bloom-pattern radial bursts, and denser projectile waves than Moldsmal.
- ACT / Spare: Standard HP-based spare. Impress ACT may affect behavior.
- Implementation notes: Radial burst spawners with bloom effects. Larger hitboxes than base molds. Tuned for Hard Mode difficulty.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Moldessa

