### 32) Moldsmal

- Location: Ruins
- Quick summary: Common slime enemy with simple drop attacks and exploding pellets.
- Attacks / Behavior: Zigzag vertical pellet drops; bomb pellets that explode mid-air into radial bursts.
- ACT / Spare: Impress or Flirt to spare. Low HP allows easy defeat.
- Implementation notes: Zig-zag drop patterns with sine offsets. Timed bomb projectiles spawn radial child projectiles on explosion.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Moldsmal

