### 35) Muffet

- Location: Hotland (Spider Bake Sale area)
- Quick summary: Spider boss fight with pet cupcake summon and web-themed attacks. Purple soul segment.
- Attacks / Behavior: Spider projectiles in arcs; pet cupcake creates additional bullets; web patterns restrict movement. Purple soul mode active.
- ACT / Spare: Having Spider Donut/Cider from Ruins ends fight early. Otherwise survive until telegram arrives (automatic spare).
- Implementation notes: Pet as separate actor with own projectiles. Purple soul rope movement. Timed spare trigger (telegram). Shop-item flag check.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Muffet

