### 41) Royal Guards

- Location: Hotland
- Quick summary: Guard duo (01 and 02) with coordinated spear/weapon attacks.
- Attacks / Behavior: Synchronized spear thrusts, crossed weapons creating X patterns, alternating attacks leaving safe zones between strikes.
- ACT / Spare: Clean Armor on one makes the other insecure (removes team cohesion). Both must be spared via compassion ACTs.
- Implementation notes: Two-actor coordination with attack synchronization. State changes when one loses confidence. Armor state tracking.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Royal_Guards

