### 42) Sans

- Location: Judgment Hall (Genocide route boss)
- Quick summary: Extremely difficult final boss with unique mechanics. Uses Gaster Blasters, bone attacks, and dodge/KR mechanics.
- Attacks / Behavior: Teleporting bone walls, Gaster Blaster beams, gravity manipulation (soul slam attacks), and continuous damage (KR/Karmic Retribution). Never stops attacking.
- ACT / Spare: Can spare after exhausting Sans by surviving all his attacks. Spare option appears when Sans falls asleep.
- Implementation notes: Frame-perfect patterns requiring pooling optimization. KR damage system (poison-like). Menu manipulation during attacks. Dodge mechanic (Sans avoids first attack).
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Sans/In_Battle

---

### 43) Shyren

- Location: Waterfall
- Quick summary: Shy singing creature that gains confidence with encouragement; music-based attacks.
- Attacks / Behavior: Musical note projectiles in waves. Agent 01 (backup singer) can appear making attacks denser. Patterns sync to rhythm.
- ACT / Spare: Hum to encourage Shyren, leading to duet and spare. If Agent 01 appears, spare becomes easier.
- Implementation notes: Music-synchronized projectile timing. Agent 01 as optional ally modifier. Hum ACT progresses confidence state.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Shyren

