### 53) Vulkin

- Location: Hotland
- Quick summary: Volcano creature that tries to help by shooting healing fire (but misunderstands).
- Attacks / Behavior: Fireball patterns, some orange (passthrough) flames. Occasionally shoots green healing projectiles thinking it helps.
- ACT / Spare: Spare becomes available after acknowledging its efforts positively.
- Implementation notes: Mix of orange (pass-through) and normal fireballs. Occasional green healing projectile spawns. Spare via positive ACT responses.
