### 54) W. D. Gaster

- Location: Mystery/hidden (not standard enemy)
- Quick summary: Hidden character in game files; not a standard encounter. Rare random events.
- Attacks / Behavior: Not canonically fought. Fan implementations vary. No official battle exists.
- ACT / Spare: N/A - not a battle encounter in original game.
- Implementation notes: If implementing as easter egg: use glitch effects, fragmented sprites, and meta/unusual mechanics. Not canon content.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/W._D._Gaster

