### 55) Whimsalot

- Location: CORE
- Quick summary: Upgraded Whimsun with more aggressive patterns.
- Attacks / Behavior: Multiple rotating rings of insects, denser column waves, and faster projectile speeds than Whimsun.
- ACT / Spare: Pray or Console to spare. Standard HP defeat also works.
- Implementation notes: Scale up Whimsun ring mechanics with more projectiles and faster rotation. Multiple simultaneous rings.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Whimsalot

