### 56) Whimsun

- Location: Ruins
- Quick summary: Timid insect that doesn't want to fight; very low HP.
- Attacks / Behavior: Rotating ring of butterfly/moth projectiles around soul. Vertical columns of insects. Slow and predictable.
- ACT / Spare: Can spare immediately. Dies in one hit (10 HP). Most flee-prone enemy.
- Implementation notes: Rotating orbital projectiles around player. Vertical column spawners. Very low HP makes it fragile tutorial enemy.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Whimsun

