### 57) Woshua

- Location: Waterfall
- Quick summary: Clean-obsessed enemy that wants to clean the player.
- Attacks / Behavior: Water drop projectiles, horizontal water waves, soap bubble patterns. Green cleansing projectiles occasionally heal.
- ACT / Spare: Let Woshua clean you (Touch/Flex dirty areas) to spare.
- Implementation notes: Water droplet spawners. Horizontal wave hazards. Green healing bubbles mixed with damage projectiles. Clean state tracking for ACT.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Woshua

