- ACT / Spare: Call for help to summon souls. Souls weaken Flowey leading to victory.
- Implementation notes: See entry 11. Large-scale multi-phase boss with save file manipulation and soul mechanics.
- Source: https://undertale.fandom.com/wiki/Photoshop_Flowey/In_Battle

