- Attacks / Behavior: One attack animation plays but deals no damage before Mettaton NEO is one-shot by player.
- ACT / Spare: Scripted instant defeat; no real battle occurs.
- Implementation notes: See entry 27. Cinematic sequence rather than real fight. High damage dealt by player, minimal HP on NEO.
